subtitleNullable: Normal, Bacterial, and Viral Chest X-Rays
descriptionNullable:
Normal, Bacteria infected, and Virus infected chest X-Ray images for classification tasks. 
There are a total of 6 files - training and testing sets for each of the 3 classes. Each of these files is a 4-D Numpy array and images are 128x128 in size within these NumPy arrays.
Normal Training - 1341 files
Virus Training - 1345 files
Bacteria Training - 2530 files
Normal Test - 234
Virus Test - 148
Bacteria - 242
Data provided by Professor Monjur Morshed (monjurm@aust.edu)
